name: GTA: Red Deer
description: A perfect location for a gran theft auto title. The location is between 2 metropolitans Edmonton and Calgary. The corrupt oil field would derive the sub culture of the game and influence the user to make decisions that earn notoriety in the oil industry. From stealing fresh water out of an aquifer to spit roasting a blonde who posts it to social media. The news will cover it, as children were notified the next day about the "Calgary Stampede Threeway" which was across the headlines of all provincial newspapers, while some stations reported a Spitroast, children certainly had questions. The news didnt feel this was an issue, and we all know albertans are all sluts. Next time you are looking for a pit stop on the "Highway to Hell" make sure you check into the Old Westin with the greasy biker slut you can find. You will need to ring you wife and tell her youre running late on lease and need 1 more day while the biker slag rings the crack pipe. Its a picturesque vision of a world suited for a popular Grand Theft Auto title.
